title: HOUR 3 - Trent Dilfer
itunes:title: HOUR 3 - Trent Dilfer
description:
In hour 3, Colin gives props to the Chicago Bears for finally making moves to put pieces around their young QB Justin Fields. Trent Dilfer joins to talk Bears trade, Vikings trade and if Miami is ready to be Super Bowl contenders.
